text: Lili Meeuwisse (born 26 May 1959) is a Dutch rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from The Hague
